ADD docs/operations/Forecasts_Founder_Alpha_Runbook.md
ADD docs/runs/market_system_round20_verification.md
MAYBE MODIFY Round 20-touched market/forecast files to fix verification failures.
MAYBE MODIFY README docs to point to the runbook.

